room_title: Escape room "The Fear Room" by Escape Kemah in Houston
review: Zachary was our game director for the night and he did amazing! We did the Fear room and it was perfect! It was chilling and exhilarating. I definitely recommend it for larger groups. Will definitely be back to do another room.

room_title: Escape room "The Fear Room" by Escape Kemah in Houston
review: We came for our birthday to the Fear room. It was amazing. We had so much fun. We definitely plan on coming back to do the Star Wars room next time.

room_title: Escape room "The Fear Room" by Escape Kemah in Houston
review: We did the Fear room for my birthday as a party of nine and had a blast! We definitely want to try another room.
